Global Intelligent Building Management Systems (IBMS) Market Insights
Intelligent Building Management Systems (IBMS) Market size was valued at USD 23.4 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 47.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.4% from 2024 to 2030.


Intelligent Building Management Systems (IBMS) Market Overview
The global Intelligent Building Management Systems (IBMS) market is projected to reach a value of approximately $80 billion by 2025, driven by the increasing demand for energy-efficient solutions and the integration of IoT technologies. As buildings become smarter, the emphasis on enhancing occupant comfort while minimizing operational costs has resulted in a robust growth trajectory for this sector.

